(1862, 1, '2016-08-13 09:06:30', '2016-08-13 09:06:30', 'Ashika Prasai is a young student in Sydney, Australia. She has been in Sydneyfor 8 years pursuing the studies of nursing. Ashika grew up in the Jhapa, Nepalseeing her mother involved in the help making to the people in need in theneighbor, she started to envision of doing something to help in the society.Like mother, Maya Prasai, young Ashika has been raising scholarships for theneedy students in Nepals villages. She has raised scholarships for 25 studentsin Dolpa in 2015 from Nepalis diaspora in Australia. Personally, she hascontributed for 5 students in Dolpa with Sadbhaw Scholarships.', 'Ashika Prasai', '', 'publish', 'closed', 'closed', '', 'subash', '', '', '2016-09-03 16:06:14', '2016-09-03 16:06:14', '', 0, 'http://localhost/sadbhaw/?post_type=leader&#038;p=1862', 0, 'leader', '', 0);
